    "The only advanced computational process involved is the natural language processing performed by the LLM.",
    "Since cloud resources were used for all processes in this study, local resources were kept to a minimum.",
    "However, if a local LLM is introduced for security or privacy reasons, additional computational resources will be required.",
    "Given that non-LLM processes are lightweight, a small-scale web server should suffice.",
    "Three main databases are required: one for user needs, one for services, and one for upcycling cases."
